Show Notes:
[1] "Best Feeling" contained a "Smooth Criminal" (Michael Jackson) jam.
[2] "Hatti's Jam" was started by Holly Bowling solo and slowly blended into a full band performance of "When It Rains, It Poors" featuring Holly.
[3] "When It Rains, It Poors" featured Holly Bowling and Page McConnell (Phish) on keys.
[4] "Lost In The Cold" featured Scott Zwang (Dopapod) on drums
